 Fresh\n| length19 = 3:14\n\n| title20 = Line Em Up\n| writer20 = {{hlist|Carter|[[Murda Beatz|Shane Lindstrom]]}}\n| extra20 = [[Murda Beatz]]\n| length20 = 2:59\n\n| title21 = Darkside\n| writer21 = {{hlist|Carter|Hamlin|Vaidel Vidal}}\n| extra21 = {{hlist|B Ham|Smurv}}\n| length21 = 2:19\n\n| title22 = Never Mind\n| writer22 = {{hlist|Carter|Rockamore|Reese|Sheldon Ferguson|Kevin Yancey}}\n| extra22 = {{hlist|Rockamore|Bobby Keyz|Ferguson}}\n| length22 = 3:33\n\n| title23 = T.O.\n| note23 = featuring [[O.T. Genasis]]\n| writer23 = {{hlist|Carter|[[O.T. Genasis|Odis Flores]]|Harleaux|Fitch}}\n| extra23 = MonstaBeatz\n| length23 = 3:08\n\n| title24 = Wayne's World\n| writer24 = {{hlist|Carter|Manny Galvez|Adolfo Ramirez}}\n| extra24 = {{hlist|Galvez|Louie Haze}}\n| length24 = 3:45\n}}\n\n'''Notes'''\n* {{sup|{{note|a|[a]}}}} signifies a co-producer\n* {{sup|{{note|b|[b]}}}} signifies an additional producer\n* {{sup|{{note|c|[c]}}}} signifies an uncredited co-producer<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B7-in8BJ6Ar/|title=Fuse. on Instagram: \"@liltunechi \"Know You Know\" feat @2chainz \ud83d\ude08 prod by @fuse808mafia @javarsaidpickupthatbag @bobby_keyzz #Funeral\"|publisher=[[Instagram]]|date=January 31, 2020|accessdate=January 31, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B7_Mzd7n6Oc/|title={{!}} Natra {{!}} on Instagram: \"Track 18 prod by @prxzx and me \u2757\"|publisher=Instagram|date=January 31, 2020|accessdate=January 31, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B7-ghniHWLo/|title=STREETRUNNER on Instagram: \"New album @liltunechi #Funeral in stores now! #NotMe Produced by @streetrunnermusic x @realkillat x Amos Roddy #Harden Produced by\u2026\"|publisher=Instagram|date=January 31, 2020|accessdate=February 3, 2020}}</ref>\n* \"Dreams\" features additional vocals by Ben Burgess\n* \"Get Outta My Head\" interpolates \"The Boy With The Black Eyes\" by XXXTENTACION\n\n'''Sample credits'''\n* \"Mahogany\" contains samples from \"Bass Song\", written and performed by [[Eryn Allen Kane|Eryn Kane]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/lil-wayne-funeral/|title=Lil Wayne: Funeral Album Review|website=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]|last=Pearce|first=Sheldon|date=February 3, 2020|accessdate=February 4, 2020}}</ref>\n* \"Clap for Em\" contains samples from \"[[Triggerman (beat)|Drag Rap (Triggerman)]]\", written by Orville Hall and Phillip Price, as performed by The Showboys.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://genius.com/a/lil-waynes-clap-for-em-samples-the-showboys-drag-rap-triggerman|title=Lil Wayne's \"Clap For Em\" Samples The Showboys' \"Drag Rap (Triggerman)\"|website=[[Genius (website)|Genius]]|last=Kelley|first=Caitlin|date=February 2, 2020|accessdate=February 4, 2020}}</ref>\n*\"Harden\" contains samples from \"Love Me or Leave Me\", written by Donald Breedlove, Herb Pilhofer and Napoleon Crayton, as performed by Band of Thieves. Found and cleared through Tracklib.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tracklib.com/blog/the-tracklib-sample-on-lil-waynes-funeral|title=The Tracklib Sample on Lil Wayne\u2019s new No. 1 Album \u2018Funeral\u2019 {{!}} Tracklib Blog|date=2020-01-31|website=Tracklib|language=en-US|access-date=2020-02-11}}</ref>\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from Tidal.<ref name=\"Tidal\"/>\n\n'''Musicians'''\n* Jonathan Buice \u2013 string arranger {{small|(track 1)}}, keyboards {{small|(track 1)}}\n* Memru Renjaan \u2013 guitar {{small|(track 1)}}, electric bass {{small|(track 1)}}\n\n'''Technical'''\n* Matthew Testa \u2013 engineering {{small|(tracks 1\u20135, 7, 8, 10, 12, 15\u201320, 23, 24)}}\n* Manny Galvez \u2013 engineering {{small|(tracks 1\u20137, 9\u201316, 18, 20\u201324)}}\n* Jeff Edwards \u2013 engineering {{small|(tracks 8, 9, 13)}}\n* Mailbox \u2013 engineering {{small|(track 10)}}\n* EJ \u2013 engineering {{small|(tracks 11, 22)}}\n* Chef \u2013 engineering {{small|(track 14)}}\n* Steven McDowell \u2013 engineering {{small|(tracks 17,