-06/|title=Top 200 Albums|work=[[Rolling Stone]]|accessdate=February 12, 2020}}</ref>\n| 1\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Lil Wayne}}\n\n[[Category:2020 albums]]\n[[Category:Lil Wayne albums]]\n[[Category:Young Money Entertainment albums]]\n{{2020s-hiphop-album-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Cameronsmiley2345qwerty", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Funeral_(Lil_Wayne_album)"}
